`‚òÖ Insight ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ`
- **`onMouseDown` stopPropagation** is critical here. The entire header div is a drag handle (`cursor: grab`, `onMouseDown={onDragStart}`). Without stopping propagation on mousedown, clicking the source path would start dragging the panel instead of triggering the click.
- **`.catch()` fallback** ‚Äî the fetch will reject if the `/__tuner/open-editor` endpoint doesn't exist (network error, not a 404). This gracefully degrades to `console.log` so users can still see and copy the path.
- **Non-null assertion `reactSource!`** is safe inside the `{sourceFile && ...}` guard ‚Äî `sourceFile` is derived from `reactSource?.displayPath`, so if `sourceFile` is truthy, `reactSource` is guaranteed non-null.
